reviewText: sadly - incorrectly formatted (everyone too skinny) - and terrible print and transfer - one of Alpha's very worst

Review of Miracle Pictures disc. Talk about being made on a shoestring, this movie must have used only half a shoestring. The cast has some good performers but they`re stuck with a terrible script and laughable sets. You can have fun smiling at miniaturized sets and inept dialog. Picture is just fair and sound is good. A curio from the past.
